<div><head>《益州記》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.2">江由左擔道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.3">按圖在陰平縣北，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.4">於城都為西。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.5">注曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.6">其道至險，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.7">自北來者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.8">擔在左肩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.9">不得度右肩也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.10">益州城，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.11">張儀所築，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.12">錦城在州南，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.13">蜀故宮號錦里。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.14">雁橋東，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.15">君平賣卜土臺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1715_CHANT_001-1a.16">高數丈。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
